question: What is peecko?
answer: Peecko is a wellness app sponsored by your Employer. Peecko brings to you short fitness videos that you can perform easily at home

question: How can I renew my membership?
answer: Your employer renew your membership automatically every month. Your employer will directly provide the business license to you

question: Do you provide 1-to-1 coaching?
answer: Some trainers provide personal coaching, the contact information is part of the description of the video
